---
layout: default
meta_description:
body_class: scrapbook
---

<section class="section section--links">
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mb-4 lg:mb-8">
      <h4 class="text-base mb-2"><a href="/" class="">Diederik</a></h4>
      <h2>/Scrapbook</h2>
      <p>"Collecting things is an art form too" ✌🏻</p>
      <p class="text-xs"><strong>Note: These images are NOT mine, but reblogged from <a href="https://tumblr.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Tumblr</a>.</strong></p>
      <p class="text-sm font-800"><a href="https://www.tumblr.com/follow/dydric" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">🦩 Follow me @ Tumblr</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap mb-4 lg:mb-8">
      {%- for i in range(0, 840) -%}
        {%- set item = import.tumblr[i] -%}
        {%- if item.type == 'photo' -%}
          <div class="w-1/3 sm:w-1/4 md:w-1/5 lg:w-1/6 p-1 flex flex-wrap items-end relative">
            <img src="{{ item.photo }}" loading="lazy" class="w-full m-0 block" data-action="zoom" data-original="{{ item.photo }}">
            <a href="{{ item.url }}" target="_blank" class="absolute z-20 bottom-0 right-0 block m-2 opacity-0 hover:opacity-100">
               <div class="font-600 p-1 text-mini leading-none relative">
                <span class="block relative z-10 max-w-full truncate text-grey-200 hover:text-white">Permalink</span>
                <div class="absolute z-0 top-0 right-0 left-0 bottom-0 bg-black opacity-50 rounded-sm"></div>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>


  </div>
</section>
